@startuml

actor User
participant "Manager Service" as Manager
participant "Twitter Service" as Twitter
participant "IEX Service" as IEX
queue "AWS Kinesis" as Kinesis
database "Redis" as Redis
database "MongoDB" as MongoDB
participant "Data Service" as DataService
storage "S3" as S3
participant "SKLearn Model Development" as ModelDev
participant "SKLearn Model Deployment" as ModelDeploy

User -> Manager: Start data collection
activate Manager

Manager -> Redis: Check market hours
Redis --> Manager: Market open

Manager -> Twitter: Collect tweets
Manager -> IEX: Fetch stock data

Twitter --> Kinesis: Stream tweet data
IEX --> Kinesis: Stream stock data

Kinesis --> DataService: Process streamed data
DataService -> MongoDB: Store processed data

ModelDev -> MongoDB: Fetch training data
ModelDev -> ModelDev: Train model
ModelDev -> S3: Upload trained model
ModelDev -> MongoDB: Log training metrics

ModelDeploy -> S3: Load latest model
ModelDeploy -> MongoDB: Fetch prediction data
ModelDeploy -> ModelDeploy: Make predictions
ModelDeploy -> MongoDB: Log predictions

User -> DataService: Request analysis
DataService -> MongoDB: Fetch data
DataService --> User: Return analysis results

Manager -> Redis: Update feature flags
Manager -> Redis: Publish logs/events

deactivate Manager

@enduml